,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:25:56.000Z","msg":"香港三權已合作，如果無埋第四權就玩撚完<br />\n多謝記者<br />\n手足都要尊重記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncctvb除外"},{"pid":"980a835ffab1315b22ebeead282cde7ad69da3aa","tid":1728592,"uid":260371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3591c9ac2e7f8e9be8243d95f3094cbff1c78001","tid":1728592,"uid":3786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:49:20.000Z","msg":"我記得早幾日睇緊中大live嘅人叫個記者唔好再影大頭，但個記者仍然影，佢地做live時睇唔到回應。你話我分化又好點都好，我覺得蘋果至少有兩個記者真係鬼鬼地，其次傳媒有佢地嘅立場好正常，大公文匯01有立場，立場，蘋果都會有立場，唔係叫佢地唔報學生嘅問題，但唔好響live影曬大頭同學生部署俾popo睇啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"但亦都因為佢係蘋果，所以大家先比佢跟得咁貼<br />\n<br />\n不過蘋果明明知道但都冇報導中大裡面內訌嘅嘢，算係咁。"},{"pid":"2600f68dff18bdaff461f11d08e6280c5e99c65f","tid":1728592,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"推，認清蘋果真面目"},{"pid":"1f21b96e4b8aa66b66875b6f1884a196290ff90b","tid":1728592,"uid":3786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2600f68dff18bdaff461f11d08e6280c5e99c65f","tid":1728592,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"推，認清蘋果真面目"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"又唔係全部記者都係咁<br />\n有啲蘋果記者都好好<br />\n我觀察係有兩個特別有問題<br />\n一個xx麟，一個xx婷<br />\n手足可以留意下，睇下係咪真係有問題<br />\n定只係我多心"},{"pid":"8e9a32f51d44bd41b990cfbf4d0bfa4b154c98b5","tid":1728592,"uid":77461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"不如認清 前線有部分人好似老黑咁<br />\n見人就屌 仲要下下講老母 有時真係好難聽 駁嘴即被圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65f1296f40f9a76b6408317e2bfbc90fc6aa5f4","tid":1728592,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e9a32f51d44bd41b990cfbf4d0bfa4b154c98b5"